60
00:03:37.420 --> 00:03:41.280
resolved tumor maps describing transitions in cancer for use by

61
00:03:41.340 --> 00:03:42.700
the cancer research community.

62
00:03:44.400 --> 00:03:48.260
Some of the important discoveries include one study which examined the

63
00:03:48.280 --> 00:03:52.100
