80
00:04:54.420 --> 00:04:58.060
Additionally, discovery of rare transitional dedifferentiated or

81
00:04:58.120 --> 00:05:01.740
plastic tumor cell types often conserved across tumor subtypes and

82
00:05:01.780 --> 00:05:03.400
correlated with the poor outcome.

83
00:05:04.080 --> 00:05:04.640
In addition,

84
00:05:05.580 --> 00:05:09.540
the study addressed the deep exploration of stroma immune and immune cell

85
00:05:09.600 --> 00:05:13.380
interactions. So far, HTAN has led to more than

86
00:05:13.500 --> 00:05:17.460
200 publications and preprints, with 20-plus primary atlas

87
00:05:17.520 --> 00:05:21.420
