01:15:43.902 --> 01:15:47.802
immune cells and tried to do a large atlas, again, of immune

1256
01:15:47.862 --> 01:15:51.322
cell signatures across the spectrum, healthy, MGUS, smoldering, myeloma.

1257
01:15:51.642 --> 01:15:55.362
But because we also have the single-cell sequencing of the tumor cells, now we can

1258
01:15:55.402 --> 01:15:59.002
look at the interaction between both of those types of

1259
01:15:59.062 --> 01:16:02.962
cells. So we don't have time to go over all the data, but I'll show you some

