01:16:35.602 --> 01:16:39.442
overt myeloma are the ones who have more of those granzyme B CD8

1270
01:16:39.462 --> 01:16:39.742
TEMs,

1271
01:16:40.582 --> 01:16:44.382
sort of trying to respond to the tumor cells and trying to respond to them in a

1272
01:16:44.402 --> 01:16:47.602
