1276
01:17:00.662 --> 01:17:04.282
across many of the immune cells, T cells, myeloid cells, and so on,

1277
01:17:04.602 --> 01:17:07.982
as well as other signatures that were correlating with myeloid suppressive

1278
01:17:08.022 --> 01:17:11.562
cells. And the other thing that we did was T cell

