01:17:41.462 --> 01:17:43.582
transcriptomic and proteomic level.

1288
01:17:43.622 --> 01:17:47.222
And to understand that, as we know very well, the bone marrow biopsies that we do

1289
01:17:47.262 --> 01:17:51.022
in our patients are very hard to actually look at them because we do

