1300
01:18:28.902 --> 01:18:32.882
So we spent a lot of time trying to develop a spatial proteomic method, and here

1301
01:18:32.962 --> 01:18:36.802
we used IMC, which is imaging mass cytometry,

1302
01:18:37.242 --> 01:18:40.702
and we developed 36 antibodies that would work on IMC that we

1303
01:18:40.722 --> 01:18:44.662
validated by immunohistochemistry and immunofluorescence to make sure indeed

