where you can actually recapitulate the data of the adipocytes,

1314
01:19:21.882 --> 01:19:25.242
and now look at all the cell-to-cell interactions in those patients.

1315
01:19:26.282 --> 01:19:29.922
And we decided to look in a study of 98 samples of

1316
01:19:30.302 --> 01:19:34.002
CAR-T, either cell or silta cell, so patients with multiple

1317
01:19:34.042 --> 01:19:36.542
