01:19:36.582 --> 01:19:40.022
If I take their sample before going on the CAR-T therapy, can I

1319
01:19:40.302 --> 01:19:42.882
predict whether they will respond to therapy or not?

1320
01:19:43.182 --> 01:19:47.151
And can I predict their toxicity? These are very critical questions

1321
01:19:47.222 --> 01:19:51.026
for us clinically.So the first thing we did is we started to look at those

1322
01:19:51.086 --> 01:19:54.776
